<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/4126155/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            柏杨版通鉴纪事本末套装的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5708413">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5708413/" class="title-link">中國人怎麼能讀柏楊如此毒素？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5708413"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53040554/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53040554-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53040554/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">仁義中國</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-22"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-22 09:18:01</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5708413_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我此前讀柏楊的書，老覺得他怎麼如此污蔑中國的歷史呢？  後來我百思不得其解。例如他還寫了什麽醬缸之類的。  過了十多年，等我瞭解了耶穌教之後，發現凡是耶穌教的人總是對總過的歷史和典籍進行惡毒的攻擊。於是我想，柏楊是否是耶穌信徒？  於是我去查了，果真，他是。哇，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5708413/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 10没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5708413_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5708413_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
